        <updateDate>2010-08-30T21:24:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Supports the designation of Rachel's Challenge: A Day of Kindness and Compassion.</p> <p> Honors the life and accomplishments of Rachel Scott and her challenge to start a chain reaction of kindness and compassion.</p> <p> Recognizes Rachel's Challenge for delivering her legacy to the world.</p> <p> Remembers the victims of the Columbine school tragedy, their families, friends, and everyone affected by the tragedy.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Expressing support for the designation of the third Thursday of April as "Rachel's Challenge: A Day of Kindness and Compassion" in honor of the triumph and hope stemming from the life of Rachel Scott and in memoriam of the Columbine High School tragedy.</title>
